# Perform PCA
pc.xray <- pca(pdbs)
plot(pc.xray)

# Calculate RMSD
rd <- rmsd(pdbs)
## Warning in rmsd(pdbs): No indices provided, using the 204 non NA positions
# Structure-based clustering
hc.rd <- hclust(dist(rd))
grps.rd <- cutree(hc.rd, k=3)

plot(pc.xray, 1:2, col="grey50", bg=grps.rd, pch=21, cex=1)
